body:
I got floating point exception (core dump) on the following test code.

```
module test;
    reg [31: 0] a;
    reg [31: 0] b;
    reg [31: 0] r;

always @*
begin
    r = $signed(a) / $signed(b);
    $display("%08x", r);
end

initial
begin
    a = 32'h80000000;
    b = 32'hffffffff;
end

endmodule
```
